text: Karamaly-Gubeyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Karamaly-Gubeyevsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,120 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 38 km from Tuymazy. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Karamaly-Gubeyevo
